<h6>Exploration <i class="bi bi-caret-right-fill"> </i> {{monde.name_world}} <i class="bi bi-caret-right-fill"></i> {{sous_monde.title}} <i class="bi bi-caret-right-fill"></i> {{histoire.title}}  </h6>
<hr>
<header class="banniere-lieu">
